6d • 6 days ago
Chat Prompts for Data Scientists

Maximize your efficiency by asking ChatGPT to help you:

1️⃣ Write python (e.g. machine learning, data visualization, data cleaning, regex, multithreaded code)
2️⃣ Explain code (explain SQL, Google Sheets formula)
3️⃣ Optimize code (improve speeds in in pandas and python)
4️⃣ Format code (in python, SQL, write documentation)
5️⃣ Translate code from one language to another (R<->python)
6️⃣ Explain technical concepts (to a five-year-old, to a business stakeholder)
7️⃣ Suggest ideas (suggest features to engineer, datasets, portfolio ideas)
8️⃣ Troubleshoot problem (PowerBI models)
9️⃣ Write SQL
🔟 Write other Code (R, VBA, Powershell)

By Travis Tang

#machinelearning #pandas #datascientists #sql #python #datavisualization #google #powerbi #data #business #engineer
#language #chatgpt #ai
